metadata.name: solitude 721-1
metadata.description:
The Desk #01

Sometimes we seek solitude
Sometimes solitude becomes necessity
To find answers to unsaid words
To find some more reasons to go on
Sometimes in the absence of nothingness we find everything 
~sigmax 




[This series captures what it would have been like for Satoshi Nakamoto when that person started with a revolutionary movement which in later years becomes a Digital Renaissance of Art & Tech.
The solitude covers the different setting where many of his/her work would have been done-IN SOLITUDE]

Size       : 3500x5000 pixels
Format : jpeg



Solitude721-(where the number marks the significance of  ERC721 and evolution of Digital Renaissance of Art)
